@MockServices_HostAddress = http://localhost:5121

### Obtener token OAuth
# @name getToken
POST {{MockServices_HostAddress}}/oauth/token
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

grant_type=client_credentials&client_id=bot-client&client_secret=bot-secret

### Crear ticket (requiere token)
POST {{MockServices_HostAddress}}/tickets
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{getToken.response.body.accessToken}}

{
  "name": "Juan Pérez",
  "email": "juan@email.com",
  "description": "Problema con la aplicación"
}

### Consultar ticket
GET {{MockServices_HostAddress}}/tickets/TCK-001
Authorization: Bearer {{getToken.response.body.accessToken}}

###
